    Lab Table

    lb_tbl.Rd

    Lab Table

    lb_tbl(data, measureVar, visitVar, studyDayVar, resultVar, llnVar, ulnVar)

    Arguments

    data

    long data frame such as LB or VS

    measureVar

    term column

    visitVar

    analysis visit column

    studyDayVar

    analysis day column

    resultVar

    analysis value column

    llnVar

    lower limit column

    ulnVar

    upper limit column

    Value

    an lineplot created with ggplot

    htmlwidget Event timeline plotly object

    Examples

    data <- safetyData::adam_adlbc %>%
  dplyr::filter(
    .data$USUBJID == sample(unique(.data$USUBJID), 1)
  )

data %>%
  lb_tbl(
    measureVar = "PARAM",
    visitVar = "AVISIT",
    studyDayVar = "ADY",
    resultVar = "AVAL",
    llnVar = "A1LO",
    ulnVar = "A1HI"
  )
